Detailed Description

Description:
: Test the TA cryptographic functions TEE_DigestUpdate, TEE_DigestDoFinal, TEE_SetOperationKey, TEE_MACInit, TEE_MACCompareFinal, TEE_MACComputeFinal, TEE_AsymmetricEncrypt, TEE_AsymmetricDecrypt, TEE_AsymmetricSignDigest, TEE_AsymmetricVerifyDigest, TEE_GenerateKey, TEE_AllocateOperation, TEE_FreeOperation, TEE_CipherInit, TEE_CipherDoFinal
